# The packaged harness binary is built locally per platform, not committed.
# `bash plugins/mutagen/scripts/build_harness_binary.sh --release` puts the
# binary at this path; consumers fetch it from a GitHub Release or build it
# themselves. Tracking it bloats clones and ships the wrong architecture to
# half the audience.
bin/mutagen-harness
bin/mutagen-harness.exe
